                        "displayName": "Antoine Pitrou",
                        "active": true,
                        "timeZone": "Europe/Paris"
                    },
                    "body": "If you want to use unsafe appends, then yes, you need to know an upper bound (and preferably a reasonable one if you don't want to overallocate too much). Otherwise, you should use normal appends (but even then, {{Reserve}} and {{ReserveData}} are useful to limit the number of resizes).",
